{"tid":1182849,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藝人李兆基肝癌擴散 搶救無效病逝","createTime":"2019-06-02T13:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T13:11:59.000Z","uid":33456,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"191260cbbb53a441b57093917f430df3492db7a8","tid":1182849,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:01:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_673367_0 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_673367_0%20&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJIxx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=db9bae48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_673367_0%20&h=725192fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_673367_0 </a><br />\n<br />\n藝人李兆基，前黑幫「慈雲山十三太保」成員李兆基，江湖綽號「高飛」，因肝癌擴散致肺部，搶救無效，下午六時三十分在伊利沙伯醫院病逝，終年69歲。李兆基在3月8日與拍拖超過二十年的女友結婚，三個月後迎來惡耗。<br />\n<br />\n李兆基演活江湖惡人、古惑仔的角色，經典作品包括《古惑仔》的吹水基，以及《黑獄斷腸歌》等角色。"},{"pid":"3ee8cc766dab26fd2448df06e6603777769897b3","tid":1182849,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"撈偏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35ccef55065248ba135823084b06b965350cff1","tid":1182849,"uid":33456,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/18/LAM.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20110607075657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F18%2FLAM.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20110607075657&h=417a7c20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6497b48fe